找到和最大的子序列 <pre><code>int MaxSubsequenceSum(const int A[], int N){ 
    int ThisSum, MaxSum, j; 
    ThisSum = MaxSum = 0; 
    for (j = 0; j &lt; N; j++){ 
        ThisSum += A[j]; 
        if (ThisSum &gt; MaxSum) 
            MaxSum = ThisSum; 
        else if (ThisSum &lt; 0) 
            ThisSum = 0;
    }  
    return MaxSum; 
} 
</code></pre> <p>这个算法的复杂度为 \(T(N) = O(N)\) 。</p>

二分查找 Binary Search <pre><code>int BinarySearch (const ElementType A[], ElementType X, int N){ 
    int  Low, Mid, High; 
    Low = 0;  
    High = N - 1; 
    while (Low &lt;= High){ 
        Mid = (Low + High) / 2; 
        if (A[Mid] &lt; X) 
            Low = Mid + 1; 
        else if (A[Mid] &gt; X) 
            High = Mid - 1; 
        else 
            return  Mid;  
    }  
    return NotFound;  
} 
</code></pre> <p>这个算法的复杂度为 \(T(N) = O(\log{N})\) 。</p>
